Have only tested on Tampermonkey for Chrome.  For best results, use that.

1. Download Tampermonkey for Chrome

  https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo?hl=en
  

2. Install the script

  https://github.com/momphis/jd-chat-help/raw/master/jd-chat-help.user.js
  
contact momphis.justdice@gmail.com if you have issues.
